partnerDetails.about: RMS Measurement & Control offers a complete product range incorporating brands such as ABB, Schneider Electric, Electro Mechanica and Circutor.  We offer solutions for distribution, automation, power monitoring and power factor correction. We have over 10 Years’ experience in electrical design and manufacturing. This allows us the ability to manufacture individual solutions to each individual client’s needs.
